    <h1>Generative Engine Optimization (GEO)</h1>
    <p class="description">The practice of optimising content to be cited by AI-powered search engines — Google AI Overviews, ChatGPT, Perplexity, and Gemini. AI Overviews now appear in <strong>50%+ of Google searches</strong>. And 97% of citations come from pages already ranking in the top 20.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
          <span class="meta-author-role">Marketing Head · theStacc</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="meta-divider"></div>
